column5: Hi Frank I have a question for you. We are thinking of going to lake kashabowie or lac des mile lac, which one would you recamend to us? And maybe the name of a couple differance resorts there. Thanks you very much for any help, Tim
Hello Tim.........Send me an e-mail and I'll see if I can help you out. Frank
Hi Tim,I may be able to help you out also. Frank fishes Lac a lot and I had a spot on Kashabowie for 5 years. Send me an email.Roger Mayer.
